descriptionHTML:
Beautiful analog Watch Face for Android Wear devices.

This watch face includes 5 colorful free themes to choose from. No configuration utility needed, change themes directly by taping on the watch face!

★ Tap on the Watch Face to cycle through themes
★ Choose between 5 colorful themes
★ Works on both round and square devices
★ Supports ambient mode
